{{fr/Traduction|en/Manual/Transparency options|0}}


This option will toggle the display of buildings.  When enabled, buildings will appear transparent, to allow you to see what is behind them so that you can effectively construct your roads and tracks. A quicker way of toggling transparent buildings is to simply press X on your keyboard.
